---
title: Sticky Beef & Veggie Udon Stir-Fry with Crispy Shallots
description: The perfect sauce is here, so make room in your pan for an teriyaki sauce that can take a beef and veggie stir-fry to stardom. Sealing this stir-fry’s rightful place are udon noodles - we give it a gold star for sure!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6594a322b6e284551035ad42-7cf13ce6.jpeg
